    body
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-light.bg-primary
            a.navbar-brand(href='#') My Website
            button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                span.navbar-toggler-icon
            #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
                ul.navbar-nav.mr-auto
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link(href='/') Home
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link(href='/about') About
        .container
            .row.justify-content-md-center
                .col.col-ms-12.col-md-10.col-lg-8.col-xl-6
                    .card.border-primary
                        .card-header 👩🏻‍💻 Create Message ✨
                        .card-body
                            form(method='post', action='/create/post')
                                .form-group
                                    label(for='title') Title
                                    input#title.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Type in your title', name='title')
                                .form-group
                                    label(for='content') Message
                                    textarea#content.form-control(placeholder='Type in your message', rows='3', name='content')
                                button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') Post New Message
            .row.justify-content-md-center
                .col.col-ms-12.col-md-10.col-lg-8.col-xl-6
                    .card.border-primary
                        .card-body
                            h4.card-title 陋室銘 😉
                            p.card-text
                            span.text-primary 山不在高，有仙則名；水💧不在深，有龍 🐉則靈。斯是陋室，惟吾德馨詞解。苔痕上階綠，草🌱色入簾青；談笑有鴻儒詞解，往來無白丁詞解。可以調素琴詞解，閱金經；無絲竹之亂耳，無案牘詞解之勞形詞解。南陽諸葛廬詞解，西蜀子雲亭詞解。孔子云：「何陋之有詞解？」
